: : Rodimus Prime : :

Rodimus Prime: I understand. Nightlight and I will move into your perimeter when you lower you deflector shields. After the barage of turret fire we&#39;ll stand by to fight if they are still coming at that time.

Rodimus looked at Nightlight, assuring himself that she was as ready as he was. Roddy stands by for the shields to drop...


rm2kmidi &lt;kraftlos@...&gt; wrote:
As soon as Salveo saw who it was at their door, he grew excited.

&quot;Hello, we would like to lower the shields.  We are going to prepare an asault on those minions, using our turrets, if you would assist us, then we can talk.   Your girl is safe, and we want to get her back to you.   So if you&#39;re ready, lets comense with the plan.&quot; 

::Meanwhile::

Ravenchief sat back in the CR chamber and let it close around him.

Guardia got near the door and held up her shield, she knew that she&#39;d be needing it again.  Salveo came up to the door as well.  The troopers manned the turrets.  They all awaited a response from the maximals outside. 

OOC: I dont&#39; know if Kenzo fights or not, but if he does we could use him!


On 9/8/05, Richard Allen &lt;roborick007@...&gt; wrote: : : Rodimus Prime : :

Rodimus addressed Salveo.

Rodimus Prime: That little girl is my daughter. My wife and I came looking for her. We are Maximals. We&#39;ll help you deal with these Minions. I have had experience dealing with Minions and Unicron.

Rodimus transformes to his robot mode. All of the Maximals outside should now be able to see his Autobot insignia. Any that are knowlegable about the Great Wars or the Neo Beast Wars should realize who he is.


rm2kmidi &lt;kraftlos@...&gt; wrote:
&quot;Salveo here, We are in Alert mode... we had a rescue mission to for a girl that had wandered off.  The mission was a sucess but they were attacked by about 5 minions.  We had a hard time getting them back.  Though I&#39;m begining to wonder if they&#39;ve forgotten about us.  What brings you here?&quot; 


::Meanwhile::

&quot;Just go into my room then, it should have my name on the door.  I&#39;ll come back for you when the fighting is over.&quot; said Guardia.

She waved goodbye and headed for the front of the base.


On 9/6/05, Airly &lt;airly2002@...&gt; wrote: Elita:
&quot;But... I don&#39;t have any room...&quot;said Elita among sobs&quot;I jsut arrive here and... left and started all the mess&quot;
&quot;That&#39;s.....good.....&quot; he said, then collapsing on the floor and going unconscious.


::Meanwhile::

Elita, can you go back to your room.  I need to help them take care of those bad people who were chasing us.  Can you stay there until I come back for you?&quot; asked Guardia as they approached the barracks section of the base. 


